ype="main"&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;milestone spanTo="#c56-0066.05" unit="tei:head"/&gt;Chap. 8&lt;hi rend="sup"&gt;&lt;hi rend="underline"&gt;th&lt;/hi&gt;&lt;/hi&gt;&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0066.05"/&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;one </rdg></app>of my first duties on my recovery was to introduce Clerval to the <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">several </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;add place="sublinear"&gt;&lt;metamark function="insert"&gt;^&lt;/metamark&gt;&lt;/add&gt;&lt;add place="superlinear"&gt;several&lt;/add&gt; </rdg></app>professors of the university. <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">In </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">And in </rdg></app>doing <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">this, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">this </rdg></app>I <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">underwent </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">under &lt;lb/&gt;went &lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;torments&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>a kind of rough <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">usage, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">usage &lt;lb/&gt;&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;that&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>ill <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;befitten&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>befitting the wounds <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">that my </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;add place="intralinear"&gt;that&lt;/add&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;my </rdg></app>mind had sustained. Ever since the fatal <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">night, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">night – </rdg></app>the end of my <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">labours, and the </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">labours &amp;&lt;lb/&gt;the </rdg></app>beginning of my <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">misfortunes, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">misfortunes &lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;&lt;unclear&gt;(&lt;/unclear&gt;&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>I had conceived a violent antipathy even to the name of <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">natural philosophy. </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;Chemistry&lt;/del&gt;&lt;add place="superlinear"&gt;Natural Philosophy&lt;/add&gt;. </rdg></app>When I was otherwise quite restored to <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1831">health, </rdg><rdg wit="#f1823 #fMSc56">health </rdg></app>the sight of <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">a chemical </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;add hand="#pbs" place="intralinear"&gt;a&lt;/add&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;Chemical </rdg></app>instrument <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">would renew </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;delSpan rend="strikethrough" spanTo="#c56-0066.02"/&gt;brought on &lt;lb/&gt;again&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0066.02"/&gt;&lt;add hand="#pbs" place="superlinear"&gt;renewed&lt;/add&gt;&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0066.01"/&gt; </rdg></app>all <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">the </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;add place="sublinear"&gt;&lt;metamark function="insert"&gt;^&lt;/metamark&gt;&lt;/add&gt;&lt;add hand="#pbs" place="superlinear"&gt;the </rdg></app>agony of my <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">my&lt;add place="sublinear"&gt;&lt;metamark function="insert"&gt;^&lt;/metamark&gt;&lt;/add&gt; </rdg></app>nervous <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">symptoms. Henry </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">symtoms. &lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;Lo&lt;/del&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;Henry </rdg></app>saw <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">this, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">this </rdg></app>and had <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">removed all </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;packed up&lt;/del&gt;&lt;add place="superlinear"&gt;removed&lt;/add&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;all </rdg></app>my <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">apparatus </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;machines&lt;/del&gt;&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;in a chest&lt;/del&gt;&lt;add place="superlinear"&gt;apparatus </rdg></app>from my <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">view. He </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;che&lt;/del&gt; view&lt;/add&gt; he </rdg></app>had also changed my <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">apartment; </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;room&lt;/del&gt;&lt;add place="superlinear"&gt;apartment,&lt;/add&gt; </rdg></app>for he perceived that I had acquired <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">a </rdg></app>dislike <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">for </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">to </rdg></app>the room which had previously been my <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">laboratory. </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">workshop. </rdg></app>But these cares of Clerval were <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">made </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;thrown away&lt;/del&gt;&lt;add hand="#pbs" place="superlinear"&gt;made </rdg></app>of no avail when I visited the professors. <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">even my excellent </rdg></app>M. Waldman inflicted torture when he <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">praised, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">praised </rdg></app>with <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;the&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>kindness and warmth, the astonishing progress <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">that </rdg></app>I had made in the sciences. He soon perceived that I <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">disliked </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">dislike&lt;add hand="#pbs" place="intralinear"&gt;d&lt;/add&gt;&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;of&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>the <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">subject; </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">subject, </rdg></app><app><rdg wit="#f1818">but, </rdg><rdg wit="#f1823 #f1831 #fMSc56">but </rdg></app>not guessing the real <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">cause, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">cause </rdg></app>he attributed my <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">feelings to modesty, and </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">feelings&lt;/add&gt;&lt;/zone&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;to modesty &lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;on hearing myself praised&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/zone&gt; &lt;/surface&gt; &lt;surface&gt; &lt;graphic&gt; &lt;/graphic&gt;&lt;zone type="main"&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;he therefore&lt;/del&gt;&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0067.01"/&gt;&lt;zone corresp="#c56-0067.01" type="left_margin"&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;add&gt;and&lt;/add&gt;&lt;/zone&gt; </rdg></app>changed the subject from my <app><rdg wit="#f1818">improvement </rdg><rdg wit="#f1823 #f1831 #fMSc56">improvement, </rdg></app>to the science itself, with <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;an&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>a <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">desire, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">desire </rdg></app>as I evidently <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">saw, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">saw </rdg></app>of drawing <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;friend&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>me out. <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;K&lt;/del&gt;&lt;delSpan rend="strikethrough" spanTo="#c56-0067.02"/&gt;Kind &lt;lb/&gt;friend he tortured me without&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0067.02"/&gt;&lt;delSpan rend="strikethrough" spanTo="#c56-0067.03"/&gt;but &lt;lb/&gt;it&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0067.03"/&gt;&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;How cruel is&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>What could I do? He meant to <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">please, and </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">please &lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;and&lt;/del&gt;&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;me&lt;/del&gt;&amp; </rdg></app>he <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">tormented me. I </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;tortured&lt;/del&gt;&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0067.04"/&gt;&lt;zone corresp="#c56-0067.04" type="left_margin"&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;add&gt;tormented&lt;/add&gt;&lt;/zone&gt; me &lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;it was&lt;/del&gt;&lt;add place="superlinear"&gt;I </rdg></app>felt as if he <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">had placed carefully, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;had&lt;/del&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0067.05"/&gt;&lt;zone corresp="#c56-0067.05" type="left_margin"&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;add&gt;placed &lt;/add&gt;&lt;/zone&gt;carefully </rdg></app>one by <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">one, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">one &lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;placed&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>in my view those instruments which were to be afterwards used in putting me to a slow and cruel <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;dre&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>death. I writhed under his words, yet dared not <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">exhibit </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">shew &lt;lb/&gt;&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;my&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>the pain I felt. Clerval, whose eyes and feelings were always quick in discerning the sensations of <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">others, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">others </rdg></app>declined the <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">subject, alleging, in excuse, his total ignorance; and </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">subject alledging &lt;add place="sublinear"&gt;&lt;metamark function="insert"&gt;^&lt;/metamark&gt;&lt;/add&gt;&lt;add place="superlinear"&gt;his&lt;/add&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;ignorance &amp; </rdg></app>the conversation took a more general turn. I thanked <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">my friend </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">him </rdg></app>from my heart, but I did not speak. I <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">plainly </rdg></app>saw <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">plainly </rdg></app>that he was surprised, but he never attempted to draw my secret from <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">me; </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">me, </rdg></app>and although I loved him with a mixture of <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">affection </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;love&lt;/del&gt;&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0067.07"/&gt;&lt;zone corresp="#c56-0067.07" type="left_margin"&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;&lt;add&gt;affection&lt;/add&gt;&lt;/zone&gt; </rdg></app>and reverence that knew <app><rdg wit="#f1818">nobounds, </rdg><rdg wit="#f1823 #f1831">no bounds, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">no &lt;lb/&gt;bounds, </rdg></app>yet I could never <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;&lt;unclear&gt;pr&lt;/unclear&gt;&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>persuade myself to confide to him that event which was so often present to my <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">recollection, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;lb/&gt;thoughts, </rdg></app>but which I feared the detail to another would only impress more deeply. <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;/surface&gt; </rdg></app>&lt;/p&gt; &lt;p&gt; <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">M. </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;/graphic&gt;&lt;zone type="main"&gt;&lt;milestone unit="tei:p"/&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;M&lt;hi rend="sup"&gt;r&lt;/hi&gt;. </rdg></app>Krempe was not <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">equally docile; and in </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;add place="sublinear"&gt;&lt;metamark function="insert"&gt;^&lt;/metamark&gt;&lt;/add&gt;&lt;add place="superlinear"&gt;equally&lt;/add&gt; docile &lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;yet&lt;/del&gt;&lt;add place="superlinear"&gt;&amp;&lt;/add&gt;&lt;delSpan rend="strikethrough" spanTo="#c56-0068.02"/&gt;weak &lt;lb/&gt;as </rdg></app>my <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">condition at that time, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">illness had made me&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0068.02"/&gt;&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0068.03"/&gt;&lt;zone corresp="#c56-0068.03" type="left_margin"&gt;&lt;addSpan hand="#pbs" spanTo="#c56-0068.04"/&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;in my then &lt;lb/&gt;condition </rdg></app>of almost <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">insupportable sensitiveness, </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">in&lt;lb/&gt;supportable&lt;lb/&gt;sensitiveness&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0068.04"/&gt;&lt;/zone&gt;&lt;anchor xml:id="c56-0068.01"/&gt; </rdg></app>his harsh blunt <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">encomiums </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">econiums </rdg></app>gave me even more pain <app><rdg wit="#fMSc56">&lt;del rend="strikethrough"&gt;that&lt;/del&gt; </rdg></app>than the benevolent approbation of M. <app><rdg wit="#f1818 #f1823 #f1831">Waldman. “D—n the fellow!” </rdg><rdg wit="#fMSc56">Waldman —"Dam&lt;add place="intralinear"&gt;n&lt;/add&gt;&lt;lb/&gt;"the 